er h-3 w-full rounded\"></div><div class=\"skeleton-shimmer h-3 w-3/4 rounded\"></div><div class=\"skeleton-shimmer h-3 w-5/6 rounded\"></div></div></div></div></div></div><!--/$--></main><section aria-label=\"Notifications alt+T\" tabindex=\"-1\" aria-live=\"polite\" aria-relevant=\"additions text\" aria-atomic=\"false\"></section></div><footer class=\"glass-card mt-auto rounded-none border-t-0 border-t relative\"><div class=\"container mx-auto px-4 py-12 relative z-10\"><div class=\"grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 lg:grid-cols-5 gap-8 md:gap-8\"><div class=\"col-span-2 md:col-span-3 lg:col-span-1 space-y-4\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"><div class=\"h-8 w-8 rounded-full bg-[#0D8A5C] flex items-center justify-center\"><span class=\"text-white font-bold text-sm\">PA</span></div><button class=\"font-bold text-xl text-[#0D8A5C] hover:text-[#0D8A5C]/80 transition-colors cursor-pointer bg-transparent border-none outline-none\" aria-label=\"PostAll branding\">PostAll</button></div><p class=\"text-sm text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed\">The all-in-one marketplace platform. Post tasks, find work, buy and sell items, and access 24 powerful tools — all in one place. No signup required to browse.</p><div class=\"flex items-center gap-1 pt-2\"><span class=\"text-xs text-muted-foreground\">A product of</span><button class=\"font-bold text-sm tracking-widest text-[#0D8A5C] hover:text-[#0D8A5C]/80 transition-colors cursor-pointer bg-transparent border-none outline-none\" aria-label=\"O.L.H.M.E.S branding\">O.L.H.M.E.S</button></div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-6\"><div class=\"h-10 w-10 rounded-full bg-[#0D8A5C]/10 flex items-center justify-center hover:bg-[#0D8A5C]/20 transition-colors cursor-pointer\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-twitter h-5 w-5 text-[#0D8A5C]\" aria-hid