is information. Additionally, we collect information from third-party sources such as payment processors, identity verification services, and social media platforms when you choose to link them to your account.\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed\",\"children\":\"When you use our built-in tools such as Proof Cam, Safe Spots, or the messaging system, we may collect additional data including timestamped photos, geolocation data, message content, and tool usage analytics. This data is stored securely and used solely for the purposes of facilitating transactions, resolving disputes, and improving our safety features.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"$L21\",null,{\"className\":\"my-8\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"id\":\"how-we-use\",\"className\":\"scroll-mt-24 mb-10\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"text-2xl font-bold mb-4 flex items-center gap-2\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"data-slot\":\"badge\",\"className\":\"inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-md border px-2 py-0.5 font-medium w-fit whitespace-nowrap shrink-0 [&>svg]:size-3 gap-1 [&>svg]:pointer-events-none focus-visible:border-ring focus-visible:ring-ring/50 focus-visible:ring-[3px] aria-invalid:ring-destructive/20 dark:aria-invalid:ring-destructive/40 aria-invalid:border-destructive transition-[color,box-shadow] overflow-hidden [a&]:hover:bg-accent [a&]:hover:text-accent-foreground border-emerald-300 text-emerald-700 text-xs\",\"children\":\"2\"}],\"How We Use Information\"]}],\"$L22\",\"$L23\",\"$L24\"]}],\"$L25\",\"$L26\",\"$L27\",\"$L28\",\"$L29\",\"$L2a\",\"$L2b\",\"$L2c\",\"$L2d\",\"$L2e\",\"$L2f\",\"$L30\",\"$L31\",\"$L32\",\"$L33\",\"$L34\"]}]\n16:[\"$\",\"$L35\",null,{\"children\":[\"$L36\",[\"$\",\"$L37\",null,{\"promise\":\"$@38\"}]]}]\n17:[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"skeleton-shimmer h-8 w-24 rounded-lg\"}]\n18:[\"$\",\"div\",\"1\",{\"className\":\"bg-white rounded-xl border overflow-hidden\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"class